http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Bank-staff-oppose-new-career-progression-scheme/article13989635.ece

The employees of various banks staged demonstrations at their respective branches across the district here on Friday.They were opposing the new Career Progression Scheme (CPS) and protesting violation of bilateral settlement agreement by associate banks of the State Bank of India. They accused the managements of adopting “anti-worker policies” by enforcing rules and regulations applicable for SBI on employees of subsidiary banks.The nation-wide protest call was given by the All India Bank Employees’ Association (AIBEA).National General Secretary of AIBEA, Gundla Prabhakar said the new scheme is in violation of a bilateral agreement with their respective unions.